<table><tr><td>Rotaeche R, Aguirrezabala J, Balagué L, Gorroñogoitia A, Idarreta I, Mariñelarena E, Mozo C, Ruiz de Velasco E, Torcal J. Clinical practice guidelines on arterial hypertension. 2007 update. Vitoria-Gasteiz: Basque Health System-Osakidetza; 2008. 135 p. </td></tr></table>            </div>
